DATE: 2026-03-25

KEY INSIGHTS:

- Strong edge detected on BUY_NO for BETWEEN markets
- BETWEEN markets are rarely hit exactly → high probability of NO winning

- BUY_YES_STRONG signals are unreliable
- Directional predictions (greater_than / less_than) show more variance

- System tends to overestimate extreme probabilities (AI PROB too high)

- Precision risk: losses occur when temperature falls exactly in predicted range

CITY OBSERVATIONS:

- NYC: stable, good for range-based NO trades
- LA: more unpredictable, weaker directional accuracy
- Chicago: strong performance on BETWEEN NO trades

STRATEGY NOTES:

- Focus on BUY_NO for BETWEEN markets as core strategy
- Be cautious with BUY_YES_STRONG signals
- Avoid overconfidence in high AI probabilities
- Continue collecting data before adjusting rules

